    </section>
</header>
<section class="center-box cntus-box">
    <ul>
        <li class="line-1">
            <figure>
                <img src="~/mobile/images/cnt_us_1.png" alt="在线客服" title="在线客服" />
                <figcaption>在线客服</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <p>7x24小时在线服务<br />无需安装，直接交谈<br />实时为您解决问题</p>
        </li>
        <li class="line-2">
            <figure>
                <img src="~/mobile/images/cnt_us_2_1.png" alt="电话客服" title="电话客服" />
                <figcaption>电话客服</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <p>7x24小时客服热线<br />+86-755-26910992<br />如遇坐席忙请稍后再拨</p>
